[asy]
unitsize(0.8 cm);

draw((-2.5,0)--(2.5,0));
draw((0,-2.5)--(0,2.5));
draw(arc((0,0),2,0,315),red,Arrow(6));
draw((0,0)--(sqrt(2),-sqrt(2)));

dot((sqrt(2),-sqrt(2)), red);
label("$(\sqrt{2},-\sqrt{2})$", (sqrt(2),-sqrt(2)), NE, UnFill);
dot((2,0), red);
[/asy]

Therefore, the polar coordinates are $\boxed{\left( 2, \frac{7 \pi}{4} \right)}.$

